Package aa.test.selenium

Class AA04AssignNewActivitiesTest

java.lang.Object
aa.test.utils.AASeleniumManager
aa.test.selenium.AA04AssignNewActivitiesTest
@Disabled("Waiting for #1629") @TestMethodOrder(org.junit.jupiter.api.MethodOrderer.MethodName.class) class AA04AssignNewActivitiesTest extends AASeleniumManager
This tests assigning activities to private space, other projects, and the project on the page (in the right column underneath other projects). It also tests assigning more than one program at once (clicking checkboxes). It also tests the alert that pops up when the user assigns many activities. After each assignment, it checks the client-snackbar, if it is correct.
